# Change Request Cause
<kos/ChangeRequest/cause> a skos:ConceptScheme ; rdfs:label "Change Request Cause Scheme"@en .
<kos/ChangeRequest/cause/PerformanceImprovement> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Performance Improvement"@en ; skos:inScheme <kos/ChangeRequest/cause> .
