# Change Request Status
<kos/ChangeRequest/status> a skos:ConceptScheme ; rdfs:label "Change Request Status Scheme"@en .
<kos/ChangeRequest/status/Planned> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Planned"@en ; skos:inScheme <kos/ChangeRequest/status> .
<kos/ChangeRequest/status/InProgress> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "In Progress"@en ; skos:inScheme <kos/ChangeRequest/status> .
