# Notification Severity
<Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity> a skos:ConceptScheme ; rdfs:label "Notification Perceived Severity Scheme"@en .
<Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Critical> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Critical"@en ; skos:inScheme <Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity> .
<Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Major> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Major"@en ; skos:inScheme <Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity> .
